Use the standard library
This is how to triangle_area of a and h:
   Remember that area is product of a and h
   Remember that result is quotient of area and 2.000000
   The answer is result
Now you know
>>> triangle_area of 5 and 3 
7.500000
>>> triangle_area of 2 and 2 
2.000000
>>> triangle_area of 10 and 8 
40.000000